    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants, HasDataToSave, HasOptionsToSave

    public class LineFit
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements HasOptionsToSave, HasDataToSave
    The main operating class in LineFit that is called on start up and sets up the base and layout and that handles all the functions calls and methods of the program
    Since:
    <0.98.0
    Version:
    2.0
